    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the assessed factors collectively provide sufficient evidence to support the hemolysis prediction claim at MRL 3. Three factors (numerical solver error, use error, and model form) were not assessed and deferred as beyond the current project scope. The team judged that the remaining assessed evidence, including Monte Carlo UQ and bench validation, adequately supports the decision. No formal analysis was performed to demonstrate that the unassessed factors are immaterial at MRL 3.",
